17
00:01:59,000 --> 00:01:59,840
What are you...?

18
00:02:00,430 --> 00:02:01,640
In the next few days,

19
00:02:01,920 --> 00:02:03,560
Meng Li will stay
in Everlasting Peace Palace,

20
00:02:03,840 --> 00:02:06,200
