21
00:02:06,950 --> 00:02:08,150
I'm not smart.

22
00:02:08,150 --> 00:02:09,000
I'm afraid I can't...

23
00:02:09,000 --> 00:02:10,120
Since you know you're not smart,

24
00:02:10,240 --> 00:02:11,840
you need to work harder.

25
00:02:12,080 --> 00:02:13,080
Otherwise,

26
00:02:13,150 --> 00:02:14,470
how can you take care of Yuan?

27
00:02:22,590 --> 00:02:23,430
Yes,

28
00:02:23,630 --> 00:02:24,470
Your Highness.

29
00:02:24,590 --> 00:02:25,710
I invited Shancha

30
00:02:25,910 --> 00:02:27,750
to our family dinner tonight.

31
00:02:44,470 --> 00:02:45,310
Meng Li,

32
00:02:45,960 --> 00:02:47,840
