and His Majesty.

33
00:02:47,960 --> 00:02:49,310
How you forgotten

34
00:02:49,310 --> 00:02:50,360
the rules I taught you?

35
00:02:50,360 --> 00:02:51,200
Your Highness,

36
00:02:51,310 --> 00:02:52,680
isn't it inappropriate

37
00:02:52,680 --> 00:02:54,000
to let Meng Li serve the wine?

38
00:02:54,120 --> 00:02:54,960
Monsters

39
00:02:55,310 --> 00:02:57,560
have always been humble servants.

40
00:03:05,000 --> 00:03:05,840
Thanks.

41
00:03:26,120 --> 00:03:26,960
Let me do it.

42
00:03:34,870 --> 00:03:36,190
It seems she needs

43
00:03:37,240 --> 00:03:38,590
to learn the rules all over again.

44
00:03:41,400 --> 00:03:42,680
Your Highness, thanks for teaching me.

45
00:03:45,590 --> 00:03:46,430
Your Majesty.

46
00:03:52,630 --> 00:03:54,400
You'll be a perfect couple.

47
00:04:03,520 --> 00:04:04,630
I'll fill up the wine.

48
00:04:21,870 --> 00:04:22,710
(Shang You.)

49
00:04:23,310 --> 00:04:24,560
(You're almost there.)

50
00:04:25,390 --> 00:04:27,000
(You can get out of here)

51
00:04:27,430 --> 00:04:28,870
(once you get his heart.)

52
