Your Highness,
please take the medicine.

53
00:04:42,270 --> 00:04:43,160
- Your Highness!
- Your Highness!

54
00:04:44,240 --> 00:04:45,080
Your Highness!

55
00:04:45,950 --> 00:04:46,790
Your Highness.

56
00:04:48,240 --> 00:04:49,560
- Your Highness!
- Your Highness!

57
