70
00:05:22,950 --> 00:05:24,390
What misunderstanding?

71
00:05:24,750 --> 00:05:25,950
The evidence is conclusive.

72
00:05:26,430 --> 00:05:28,360
When will you stop defending her?

73
00:05:28,560 --> 00:05:29,830
- But...
- Arrest her.

74
00:05:30,480 --> 00:05:31,480
Arrest her!

75
00:05:36,750 --> 00:05:38,560
