be poisoned by Kirin's venom?)

76
00:05:45,000 --> 00:05:45,840
Your Majesty.

77
00:05:46,040 --> 00:05:47,270
Did you do it?

78
00:05:49,430 --> 00:05:50,630
Your Majesty, you don't believe me?

79
00:05:51,510 --> 00:05:53,800
You're the only silver deer monster
in the world.

80
00:05:54,360 --> 00:05:55,200
Kirin's venom

81
00:05:55,480 --> 00:05:57,390
