by a silver deer monster's essence

82
00:05:57,390 --> 00:05:58,630
to become poisonous.

83
00:05:58,630 --> 00:06:00,160
How can I believe you?

84
00:06:02,680 --> 00:06:04,240
Your Majesty,
since you don't believe me,

85
00:06:06,240 --> 00:06:07,720
I have nothing to say.

86
00:06:08,150 --> 00:06:14,400
♪I've seen the moon wax and wane♪

87
00:06:17,360 --> 00:06:18,480
(I'm so ridiculous.)

88
00:06:19,750 --> 00:06:21,750
(Why would I have expectations of you?)

89
00:06:23,630 --> 00:06:25,560
(You're an evil demon.)

90
00:06:26,270 --> 00:06:28,360
(I'm nothing but a prey to you.)

91
00:06:29,870 --> 00:06:32,510
(And I only want to get
your amber heart.)

92
00:06:33,160 --> 00:06:34,120
(We're)

93
00:06:34,680 --> 00:06:36,800
(just using each other.)

94
00:06:37,760 --> 00:06:41,640
♪My lingering memories of you♪

95
00:06:41,640 --> 00:06:44,520
♪Will melt the snow on my shoulders♪

96
00:06:44,800 --> 00:06:48,740
♪Even if I can't stop missing you♪

97
00:06:48,740 --> 00:06:50,880
♪Or prevent the flowers from falling♪

98
00:06:50,950 --> 00:06:53,160
I wanted to teach her rules,

99
00:06:53,560 --> 00:06:54,630
but I never expected

100
00:06:54,630 --> 00:06:56,430
that she'd poison me.

101
00:06:57,360 --> 00:06:58,680
Mother, rest well.

102
00:06:59,070 --> 00:07:00,560
I'll make the murderer

103
00:07:00,720 --> 00:07:01,870
pay for this.

104
00:07:14,680 --> 00:07:16,360
