105
00:07:19,190 --> 00:07:20,160
I didn't.

106
00:07:20,500 --> 00:07:23,370
♪Feeling empty inside♪

107
00:07:24,080 --> 00:07:30,230
♪Needless to say,
I still regret the mistakes I made♪

108
00:07:31,150 --> 00:07:34,370
♪Talking to the moon♪

109
00:07:34,610 --> 00:07:37,190
♪What is love♪

110
00:07:38,480 --> 00:07:39,750
You're still lying.

111
00:07:40,750 --> 00:07:43,190
You've stayed with me
and waited for so long.

112
00:07:43,480 --> 00:07:45,000
What are you up to?

113
00:07:45,680 --> 00:07:47,040
You're very smart.

114
00:07:48,160 --> 00:07:50,630
You helped me to regain my power.

115
00:07:51,270 --> 00:07:52,720
