119
00:08:01,210 --> 00:08:04,610
♪Even if I can't stop missing you♪

120
00:08:04,610 --> 00:08:07,700
♪Or prevent the flowers from falling♪

121
00:08:07,700 --> 00:08:09,810
♪I'll let the destined punishment♪

122
00:08:09,810 --> 00:08:13,120
